	changeSet(author: "Nico (generated)", id: "131557858746-1") {
		sql ("""
			insert into `brand_content` values (1,'<h4>A very good cru</h4>\r\n\r\n			<div class="clear">\r\n\r\n				<p class="caption">The wine château in the Bordeaux region where Caudalie''s story originates from dates back to 1365. It changed ownership several times throughout the centuries (including belonging to a former mayor of Bordeaux and Scotsman George Smith) before Mathilde''s parents acquired the estate in 1990 - just 3 years before Mathilde and Bertrand began growing the seeds of Caudalie.</p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n','<h2>Mathilde''s Vineyard<hr /></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>As the story goes, husband and wife founders Mathilde and Bertrand Thomas never expected to leave wine for skincare - until they met the world''s leading expert on grapevine polyphenols ("grape antioxidants" in good old English) on her family winery in 1993. Inspired by Dr. Vercauteren''s knowledge in the extraordinary benefits of the vine, the couple quickly uncorked the worlds first skincare line dedicated to the fleshy fruit.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Today, the grapes of the Château Smith Haut Lafitte can be found in a bottle of grand cru - and also in the Caudalie spa facing the vineyard.</p>\r\n','<iframe width="470" height="269" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/yffB4C666cg" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe> ','<h2>Have your grape and drink it too.<hr/></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>Homegrown in the heart of French wine country, Caudalie’s natural cosmetics line is fresh from the vine. Celebrating everything the grape has to offer, each delicate formula boasts the latest in antioxidant technology to help your skin fight against the clock. Caudalie''s products mix simplicity with refinement to refresh and hydrate your skin in the most natural of ways.</p>\r\n','Homegrown in the heart of French wine country, Caudalie’s natural cosmetics line is fresh from the vine. Caudalie''s products mix simplicity with refinement to refresh and hydrate your skin in the most natural of ways. ','Caudalie Beauty Products - Sample Caudalie Skincare With Carmine.co.uk ','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/marta.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/sotammm">@sotammm</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"I''m always amazed by natural Caudalie''s products make you feel. One of my favourite products to keep in the shower is the <strong><a href="http://www.caudalie.com/uk/corps/gommages/merlot-friction-scrub.html">Merlot Friction Scrub</a></strong>. It smells minty and refreshing and is the perfect way to wake-up in the shower in the morning."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/clement.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/clement_m">@clement_m</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"I have been trying to find the right occasion to give a bottle of Caudalie''s <strong><a href="http://www.caudalie.com/uk/corps/eau-fraiche/fleur-de-vigne.html">Fleur de Vigne fragrance</a></strong> to my girlfriend. The scent honestly will transport you to the vineyards of France during the summer. Come to think of it, kind of wish I was there now."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n'),(2,'<h4>Big name clients</h4>\r\n\r\n			<div class="clear">\r\n\r\n				<p class="caption">Daniel Sandler has done make-up for tons of our favourite celebrities, including Lisa Snowdon, Claudia Winkleman, Carly Zucker, Nell McAndrew and Myleene Klass. He even did Jade Goody''s wedding make-up. But the one celebrity he is dying to work with is Beyoncé Knowles.</p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n','<h2>Pretending to be David Bowie.<hr /></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>In an attempt to transform himself into pop icon David Bowie, Daniel first stumbled into the world of make-up as a teenager in the 1980s. Once the right look was in place, he would strut around in Chelsea and eventually met tons of other like-minded fashionistas. Enamoured with how much make-up could change a person, he ultimately decided to enrol at the London College of Fashion - and the rest is history!</p>\r\n','<object width="640" height="382" classid="clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000" id="videojugplayer"><param name="movie" value="http://www.videojug.com/player?id=ac20aacd-df46-0e7f-c643-ff0008ca7e72"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowScriptAccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.videojug.com/player?id=ac20aacd-df46-0e7f-c643-ff0008ca7e72" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="470" height="290" allowFullScreen="true" allowScriptAccess="always"></embed></object> ','<h2>Now that''s professional.<hr/></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>Developed by expert make-up artist Daniel Sandler, this range of multi-purpose, award-winning products offers glamourous, long-lasting results fit for the red carpet. From pretty pots of mineral eyeshadow to watercolour-like rouge, each of his easy-to-use materials is produced from over 20 years of industry expertise. Perfect for absolutely any canvas, slip one or more of these versatile products into your bag and take a professional with you wherever you go.</p>\r\n','Developed by expert make-up artist Daniel Sandler, this range of multi-purpose, award-winning products offers glamourous, long-lasting results fit for the red carpet. ','Daniel Sandler Makeup - Sample Daniel Sandler Products With Carmine.co.uk ','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/sarah.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/sarahmansfield1">@sarahmansfield1</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"At first, I was a little hesitant to try Daniel Sandler''s <strong><a href="http://www.urbanretreat.co.uk/beautique/product/Daniel_Sandler/Watercolour.aspx">Watercolour Fluid Blush</a></strong> because it isn''t really evident how to use a liquid blusher. But  it is actually incredibly easy to use and creates a very natural look. I recommend it to everyone."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/emma.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/emma_louise2">@emma_louise2</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"Daniel Sandler''s <strong><a href="http://www.urbanretreat.co.uk/beautique/product/Daniel_Sandler/On_The_Loose_.aspx">On the Loose powder</a></strong> is one of my all-time favourite products. It comes in 4 different shades makes your skin look flawless without giving away a sign of make-up. Plus, it''s durable and just comfortable to wear - you don''t have to worry about it getting cakey or anything."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>'),(3,'<h4>Setting-up shop</h4>\r\n\r\n			<div class="clear">\r\n\r\n				<p class="caption">Balance Me made its first big appearance at Topshop, when the store requested 200 exfoliating polishes for VIPs attending a shoe department launch. And it was in the very same store that Balance Me was given its first pop-up shop later that year. </p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n','<h2>Good enough for Claudia Schiffer.<hr /></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>It turns out that you don''t have to spend millions to look and feel like a supermodel. Claudia Schiffer is a self-proclaimed fan of Balance Me''s natural products - which she was lathering onto her belly and have helped reduce post-pregnancy stretch marks. The product she recommends most? Balance Me''s super moisturising oil to leave the skin nice and soft. We''ll take several bottles...and then some.</p>\r\n','<img src="/images/brands/balanceMe-products.jpg" /> ','<h2>Striking a natural balance.<hr/></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>There''s nothing off balance about this line of luxurious, aromatherapy-based bath, body and skincare products. Initially created by sisters Rebecca and Clare Hopkins in their kitchen, Balance Me''s award-winning relaxing range is packed with the freshest ingredients - from authentic natural extracts to high grade essential oils - and steers clear of parabens, sulfates or any other potentially harmful elements. Together with aromatherapy expert Sian Jones, the sisters have produced the ultimate candy for any bathroom. These colourful packages and delicate aromas of lavender, red mandarin, sweet rose and cirtus will leave your body and soul in just the perfect - yep, you guessed it - balance.</p>\r\n','Balance Me''s award-winning relaxing range is packed with the freshest ingredients - from authentic natural extracts to high grade essential oils - and steers clear of parabens, sulfates or any other potentially harmful elements. ','Balance Me Beauty Products - Sample Balance Me Products With Carmine.co.uk ','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/michiel.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/MKotting">@MKotting</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"My wife really likes the honey-based <strong><a href="http://www.balanceme.co.uk/bath-body/range/product-family/shiny-clean-hair/">Shiny Clean Hair line</a></strong> - and I admit that I really can''t help but use a little every now and then when I''m in the shower!"</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/roxanne.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/roxannevarza">@roxannevarza</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"I''m absolutely addicted to the <strong><a href="http://www.balanceme.co.uk/bath-body/product-family/rose-otto/rose-otto-hydrating-lip-salve/">rose otto fragrance</a></strong>. My favourite product from that line is the hydrating lip balm, which soothes and moisturises chapped lips like no other. I take with me everywhere I go!"</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>'),(4,'<h4>No chemistry on stage</h4>\r\n\r\n			<div class="clear">\r\n\r\n				<p class="caption">You don''t need a degree in chemistry in order to launch a killer cosmetics line - and Marissa is proof. theBalm''s founder didn''t study the periodic table of elements in university. Turns out she has a degree in theatre. Still, she didn''t let her diploma stop her from mixing up amazing formulas of shea butter, beeswax and castor oil. </p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n','<h2>It all began with 11 books.<hr /></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>theBalm''s origins are almost good enough to eat. Seeking a few simple yet glamorous products, founder Marissa Shipman turned to books for the answer - 11 of them to be exact. After purchasing them on Amazon, she got reading and quickly began mixing-up make-up in her kitchen. A natural success, it wasn''t long before Marissa stepped up and launched her own line.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>From concealer that does double-duty as an anti-aging treatment to mini-eyeliners that can be easily stashed in handbags and hip pockets, theBalm''s story and original products are an inspiration to anyone who ever dreamed of launching their own cosmetics line.</p>\r\n','<img src="http://www.leroseauxjoues.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/thebalm.jpg" width="470px" /> ','<h2>Not your average good girl.<hr/></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>theBalm''s fun, multi use products offer quick fixes for women on the go. With flirtatious names like Plump My Pucker and Down Boy, these fantastic formulas and striking colours come wrapped up in sexy vintage packaging. Each and every product allows you to release your inner artist and will keep you looking your best - wherever life in the fast lane takes you.</p>\r\n','theBalm''s fun, multi use products offer quick fixes for women on the go. With flirtatious names like Plump My Pucker and Down Boy, these fantastic formulas and striking colours come wrapped up in sexy vintage packaging. ','theBalm Makeup - Sample theBalm Cosmetic Products With Carmine.co.uk ','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/anais.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/anais_lombard">@anais_lombard</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"I love <strong><a href="http://www.justbeautydirect.co.uk/product/the_balm_stainiac_-_beauty_queen/">Stainiac in Beauty Queen</a></strong>. I wish my lips were naturally this colour. It leaves a sweet and sexy I''ve-just-been-eating-raspberries matte stain that lasts through lunch."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/roxanne.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/roxannevarza">@roxannevarza</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"<strong><a href="http://www.justbeautydirect.co.uk/product/thebalm_-_shady_lady_eye_shadow_liner/">The Shady Lady Shadows and Liners</a></strong> are fabulous, especially in the rich, dark colours. I guess we could call say they''re like drugs for smoky-eye addicts (yes, I''m one of them)."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n'),(5,'<h4>A nail out of water</h4>\r\n\r\n			<div class="clear">\r\n\r\n				<p class="caption">According to Trind''s experts, water actually disturbs the moisture balance in your nails. Apparently, unprotected nails actually become weaker when exposed to a little H2O as it causes the nail to shrink and swell. And you thought water was good for you!</p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n','<h2>Two weeks to perfection.<hr /></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>Delivering perfect hands and nails in just two weeks may sound a little ambitious - but that''s Trind! Appropriately named to deliver only the best results, the Perfect System will rid your dainty paws of their imperfections in record time. Overgrown or dry cuticles? Brittle nails that lack moisture? Chapped hands? Honestly, you can say "afscheid" (that''s Dutch for "goodbye") to all of it. The complete set comes with 4 different nail treatments, nail buffer and hand repair cream and is the true apex of nail science.</p>\r\n','<img src="/images/brands/trind_products.jpg" /> ','<h2>The right hand.<hr/></h2>\r\n\r\n			<p>The Dutch experts behind Trind have formulated everything you need to get the upper hand. Hardly a quick fix or a cover-up, these distinguished products are packed with complicated, scientific ingredients (uh...like acrylates copolymer, dimethiconol and mercaptopropionic acid) to provide a true maintenance program for your five-fingered friends. Complete with manicure tools and a full palette of gorgeous Caring Colours, this line offers the Perfect System for any woman (or man!) who ever wanted to show her hands.</p>','The Dutch experts behind Trind have formulated everything you need to get the upper hand. Complete with manicure tools and a full palette of gorgeous Caring Colours, this line offers the Perfect System for any woman (or man!) who ever wanted to show her hands. ','Trind Nail Products - Sample Trind Nail Products With Carmine.co.uk ','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/emma.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/Emma_Louise2">@Emma_Louise2</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"A friend of mine gave me a bottle of <strong><a href="http://www.garden.co.uk/php/showProducts.php?plu=3117629&catClr">Trind''s Quick Dry</a> </strong> for my birthday last year. You can apply it on top of any wet nail polish and it dries instantly. Literally."</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n','<section class="left"><img src="/images/icons/anais.png" /></section>\r\n\r\n						<section class="left" style="width:80%; margin-left:10px">\r\n\r\n							<p><a href="http://twitter.com/#!/anais_lombard">@anais_lombard</a></p>\r\n\r\n							<p>"I''m not usually big on nail varnish but I absolutely love Trind''s Caring Colour line. I tend to use the lighter cream-coloured shades, like <strong><a href="http://www.garden.co.uk/php/showProducts.php?plu=0614492&catClr">CC104</a> </strong>. I few brush strokes and I look like I''ve paid for a professional manicure!"</p>\r\n\r\n						</section>\r\n'),(6,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(7,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(8,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(10,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);

